Bobertron was still in the woods cloaked. He felt something was wrong. He looked up and saw Sniper shoot Pantron in the head. He got up filled with rage he powered up his energy blast and shot it at Sniper. Right after he shot it he went into beast mode. Unknowing weither he had it sniper. He grabbed pantron's corpse to see if anything could be done. He was prepared to hear or feal shots firing at him. He then saw cybershark approching.
